{"tid":1561200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開始明白 咩叫 光復香港 時代革命 你哋有感,請抒發","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:00:17.000Z","uid":299729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07cacc89625b8ca0959584a03c1aaed8d94c3fef","tid":1561200,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:43:45.000Z","msg":"大家都攰 大家都要搵食 明嘅<br />\n<br />\n無話要割蓆 只係覺得越嚟越消磨勇武嘅人數 及悲傷佢地及後的被對代<br />\n<br />\n攰既 用 和理非 和理優 課餘讀law<br />\n<br />\nThis moment, singing for our demands<br />\n<br />\n好記得第一次民間記者會 當值人回答每個人對 光復香港 時代革命 都有唔同解釋<br />\n當其時我唔認同 呢句口號 依家我覺醒喇<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以俾香港變成警察政權<br />\n<br />\n光復<br />\n係光復我哋昔日 有三權分立 有以前真ICAC 嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n時代 <br />\n係我哋青年或者係呢個時代嘅人<br />\n而唔可以正係再靠咩所謂泛民爭取民主但係一直乜鬼民主都爭取唔到嘅人<br />\n革命<br />\n係 變革 好似工業革命咁 要有一個嶄新嘅進步<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"d8c42ef15e43d9c10c89b55589602c3c60f9b696","tid":1561200,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:44:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2d506edb36fcfb080e4af1ae005ac68f652e5230","tid":1561200,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"自推20"},{"pid":"d5050f